title: I Choose Victorinox - Ryan Fibiger
transcripts:
[MUSIC PLAYING]

I made a jump from finance to butchery five years ago. We had this idea of reinventing a butcher shop.I chose Victorinox for many reasons. I think it's that the design is smart. The way that the blade flexes and the blade cuts. The different stiffnesses. I know that if I wanted a longer signature, if I wanted to be a little bit more flexible, I can pretty much do exactly what I want. Everybody here wears their knives proudly on their hips and I've never said, "You guys have to use Victorinox. That's what everybody chooses. It's the same reason that we choose the quality of meat that we choose. It's gotta be the best. My name is Ryan Fibiger. I am the owner of Craft Butchery in Westport Connecticut and I choose Victorinox.
